highlights.text: “One Right Now (with The Weeknd)” by Post Malone and The Weeknd is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #9.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “One Right Now (with The Weeknd)” is the highest at #9.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 249 weeks straight.
“SAD GIRLZ LUV MONEY Remix (feat. Kali Uchis and Moliy)” by Amaarae, Kali Uchis, and Moliy is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 129 spots at #30.
